sentence.text: Stimulation of BxPC-3, Panc-1, and cell proliferation PaCA-2 pancreatic cancer cells with angiogenesis, neutrophil apoptotic process, FGF-1, FGF-2, FGF-7, and FGF-10 growth factors caused changes in the expression of master genes regulating pancreatic development (SOX9, HNF3b, glutaminyl-tRNAGln biosynthesis via transamidation-4, GATA-6, and negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II).

entity.text: negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II
